      "content": [
        {
          "type": "output_text",
          "text": "**Voxtral Transcribe 2 by Mistral AI** dominates the top English-language X posts matching your query, with the official announcement thread from @MistralAI garnering over 2,400 likes just yesterday (Feb 4, 2026).[[1]](https://x.com/i/status/2019068826097213953)\n\nKey highlights from the release:\n- **Two models**: Voxtral Mini Transcribe 2 (batch processing with ~4% WER on FLEURS benchmark, $0.003/min, speaker diarization, word-level timestamps, context biasing, 13 languages) and Voxtral Realtime (sub-200ms configurable latency for live apps, Apache 2.0 open weights).[[2]](https://x.com/i/status/2019068832405443046)[[3]](https://x.com/i/status/2019097517569302840)[[4]](https://x.com/i/status/2019097525173850395)\n- New **Audio Playground** in Mistral Studio for instant testing (upload files, toggle diarization, etc.).[[5]](https://x.com/i/status/2019092166694383686)\n- Check the intro video and benchmarks in Mistral's thread.[[1]](https://x.com/i/status/2019068826097213953)\n\nRecent posts echo excitement: sub-200ms latency beats competitors like Whisper on cost/speed, ideal for voice agents.[[6]](https://x.com/i/status/2019094844153770143)[[7]](https://x.com/i/status/2019164546431090784) Full details: https://mistral.ai/news/voxtral-transcribe-2[[8]](https://x.com/i/status/2019184322540900726)\n\nOther hits include general speech-to-text apps (e.g., Expo voice templates[[9]](https://x.com/i/status/2018580548059312241), Raspberry Pi voice HAT[[10]](https://x.com/i/status/2017863062053851549)) and complaints about tools like Gboard.[[11]](https://x.com/i/status/2017573409916420501) No major unrelated spikes in speaker diarization or real-time transcription chatter.",
